- 按主題過濾星標，以便晚安之星與您的興趣相關

Hello hello!

We’ve followed your suggestions and have been working day and night to fix stability issues and improve call quality. Thank you for your patience.

We’ve also added a brand new voice forum! Many of you asked for this cool feature and it’s finally here! Same Goodnight fun but a whole new way to interact with the community. With the voice forum, you can:

- Post a voice note about anything you want and engage with the community!
- Create a conversation with the like-minded people around your favourite topics and make new friends!
- Use voice as well as text to reply and comment on voice forum posts!
- Post anonymously if you want to keep it private and discreet!
